high_descs: Turn left for one step, turn left again and walk to the refrigerator, turn right for three steps and turn left to face the counter and look up at the cabinets.
Open both doors on the left cabinet, take the coffee mug out of the cabinet and then shut the doors.
Bring the coffee mug down then turn around for one step, turn right for four steps and turn right to face the refrigerator.

Open the refrigerator and put the coffee mug on the second shelf, near the front edge a few inches off center to the right. and shut the door, wait a few seconds then open the fridge, take the cup out and shut the door.
Turn around for one step, turn left for two steps then turn left and stop.
Open the bottom cabinet to the right of the refrigerator and then put the cup in toward the front and shut the cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold coffee up in the bottom cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the right of the refrigerator to the counter
Open the cupboard door above and take out the cup in the cupboard
close the cupboard door, turn to the right, and carry the cup to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator door, place the cup inside the refrigerator on the shelf, close the refrigerator door, wait, open the refrigerator door, and take out the cup
Turn to the right of the refrigerator and open the lower cupboard door
Put the cup in the lower cupboard and close the door
anns.task_desc: Chill a cup and place it in the lower cupboard

high_descs: Turn around and then left. Turn right to move past the island, but turn left to face the counter.
Open the top cabinet and remove the cup. Shut the door.
Hold the cup and look down, then turn to the left and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the cup inside. Shut the door. Open the door and take the cup out. Shut the door.
Hold the cup and take a few steps to the right.
Open the bottom cabinet and place the cup inside. Shut the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Chill a cup and place it in the cabinet.
